WQL Query Runner is a free tool for testing WMI SQL queries. Developed by Uros Calakovic, except for the wizard, which was taken from here:
http://www.differentpla.net/content/2005/02/implementing-wizard-c
I would like to thank the author for making it publicly available. Also, the help file was created with a free version of HelpNDoc:
http://www.helpndoc.com/
Get the latest WQL Queru Runner version at:
http://wqlqueryrunner.codeplex.com/
